Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Book
    Book Represents a book within the library that inherits from the Resource class.
    BookTest
    Test class for the Book class that also indirectly tests the Resource class as well.
    ElectronicDevice
    Represents an electronic device within the library with data members representing the unique Id, its location in the library, the device type ( computer, tablet etc.), and whether the device is currently being used by a library member or not.
    ElectronicDeviceTest
    Test class for the ElectronicDevice class.
    ElectronicResource
    Represents an electronic resource at the library.
    ElectronicResourceTest
    Test class for the ElectronicResource class.
    Library
    Library Represents the Library object that will be used to store users, devices, and resources as well as functionality to manipulate data within these objects stored.
    LibraryMember
    Represents a member of the library with the ability to borrow and return books.
    LibraryMemberTest
    Test class for the LibraryMember class.
    LibraryTest
    Test class for the Library class.
    Resource
    Represents a resource at the library and is the parent class to ElectronicResource (online paper, pdf, e-book) and Book.
